{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"48de92cd59","title":"中共湖南日报委员会关于朱正同志被划为右派分子的改正决定(二)","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2c7b786ef3","index":0,"year":1979,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"48de92cd59"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d1b95c690e","type":"title","text":"中共湖南日报委员会关于朱正同志被划为右派分子的改正决定(二)","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"fdba044928","type":"paragraph","text":"朱正同志在本报反右派运动中被划为右派分子，受到开除公职、劳动教养的处分。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"1253c72391","type":"paragraph","text":"这次根据中共中央〔1978〕五十五号文件精神进行复查，朱正原被划为右派属于错划。经研究决定予以改正。撤销原处分。恢复原工资级别行政21级，从一九七八年十月一日起按行政21级工资发给。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"dae7d65666","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共湖南日报社委员会一九七九年三月三十日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"81a41b0584","type":"paragraph","text":"报：省委组织部、宣传部、省摘帽办、公安局","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"1314ff8f9d","type":"paragraph","text":"发：长沙市公安局、摘帽办、文艺路办事处、派出所、文艺路测绘社","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"778aa539f2","type":"subtitle","text":"附：湖南日报政治处给朱正的回信","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"7233872df0","type":"subtitle","text":"1981.06.30","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"17dc01272d","type":"paragraph","text":"同志：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"21e0c0b3a1","type":"paragraph","text":"我们根据中央和省委的指示精神，对你原被错划右派的改正问题进行了复议。现将修改后的改正决定给你一份，前所发改正文件作废。特告。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"4e685847e2","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"3dc679361d","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"ebe98b1366","type":"paragraph","text":" 湖南日报政治处1987年6月30日","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"},{"id":"a299fb37c2","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：朱正《小书生大时代》，北京大学出版社，1999年。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59"}],"page":{"id":"0ab90b5fb6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"48de92cd59","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}